'''薩奇琳清真寺'''（Şakirin Mosque）是[[土耳其|土耳其]][[伊斯坦布尔|伊斯坦布尔]]的一座清真寺，位于[[于斯屈达尔|于斯屈达尔]]区的一个墓地入口，于2009年5月7日开放。

建筑师 Hüsrev Tayla，以设计[[安卡拉|安卡拉]]的[[科札德佩清真寺|科札德佩清真寺]]著称。室内设计师Zeynep Fadıllıoğlu<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hurriyet.com.tr/pazar/5218834.asp|title=Bu Camide Ayak Kokusu Olmayacak|accessdate=2017-02-06|archive-date=2009-05-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090514053534/http://www.hurriyet.com.tr/pazar/5218834.asp|dead-url=no}}</ref>是第一位设计清真寺的女性<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.cnn.com/2014/09/23/world/meast/divine-design-the-mosque-architect/ |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2017-02-06 |archive-date=2018-10-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181014165124/http://www.cnn.com/2014/09/23/world/meast/divine-design-the-mosque-architect/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.womensagenda.com.au/talking-about/world-of-women/meet-zeynep-fadillioglu-the-first-women-to-design-a-mosque-in-modern-turkey/201306032262 |title=Zeynep Fadillioglu: First woman to design a mosque in Turkey |publisher=Womensagenda.com.au |date=2013-06-04 |accessdate=2014-06-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150203035601/http://www.womensagenda.com.au/talking-about/world-of-women/meet-zeynep-fadillioglu-the-first-women-to-design-a-mosque-in-modern-turkey/201306032262 |archive-date=2015-02-03 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.csmonitor.com/2009/0803/p17s01-algn.html|title=Mosque Modern|accessdate=2017-02-06|archive-date=2009-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090806185038/http://www.csmonitor.com/2009/0803/p17s01-algn.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

该清真寺的建造历时四年，面积10,000平方米，有两个高35米的[[叫拜楼|叫拜楼]]。它是[[土耳其|土耳其]]最[[碳中和|碳中和]]的[[清真寺|清真寺]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.tgrthaber.com/news_view.aspx?guid=%7BF6A167F0-1840-435C-BB8A-9931F88ED4E2%7D|title=Türkiye'nin En Modern Camii İbadete Açıldı|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110716214403/http://www.tgrthaber.com/news_view.aspx?guid=%7BF6A167F0-1840-435C-BB8A-9931F88ED4E2%7D|archivedate=2011-07-16}}</ref>。 

